<li>
<a href="https://support.apple.com/iphone" target="" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">iPhone Support</a> (Apple devices)</li>
<li>
<a href="https://support.google.com/android/?hl=en#topic=7313011" target="" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">Android Help</a> (Android mobile devices)</li>
</ul>
